{
  "stem": "1858.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 315.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were ordered to stand in long files, and in front of each file stood a Gestapo--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Each file of people, of each line, stood a Gestapo or an SS man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would put a stick in front of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That stick sort of served as a separation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I believe it was a mental separation as well as physical, that we were some kind of a germ and we could not approach them too close.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I was approaching that Nazi dressed in black uniform, I was thinking, who is he?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is he doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Though to me, he looked like a devil, on that day, that horrible day that I shall never forget, he and those standing there in front of us, played the role of gods.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For each of these men, of these human beings, as we called them, was deciding that day who shall live and who shall die.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all it took is a turn of a thumb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As we were approaching them, the selection was swift.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Right, left, right, left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You looked at them, and they didn't even see you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It seemed like what are they doing?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those sent to the right were young, healthy, strong.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Among them, another one of my sisters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Soon these young people were loaded on trucks and eventually they, too, were shipped to labor concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people were released, allowed to go home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those sent to the left-- among them my father, my mother, my younger sister, and myself-- were slated to be sent to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Auschwitz is a small town located not very far from my hometown, yet it has become the place where the great German scientists, architects, engineers, doctors have developed the most effective, most efficient death factory.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
